==解剖特征==
===组成===
Willis环由下列动脉组成<ref name="Purves">{{cite book | author = Purves, Dale | coauthors = George J. Augustine, David Fitzpatrick, William C. Hall, Anthony-Samuel LaMantia, James O. McNamara, Leonard E. White | title = Neuroscience, 4th Ed. | publisher = Sinauer Associates | pages = 834–5 | year = 2008 | isbn = 978-0-87893-697-7 | url = http://www.sinauer.com/neuroscience4e | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110927082419/http://www.sinauer.com/neuroscience4e/ | archivedate = 2011-09-27 | access-date = 2011-09-22 }}</ref>：
*[[大脑前动脉|大脑前动脉]]（左，右）
*[[前交通动脉|前交通动脉]]
*[[颈内动脉|颈内动脉]]（左，右）
*[[大脑后动脉|大脑后动脉]]（左，右）
*[[后交通动脉|后交通动脉]]（左，右）
此外，供应脑组织的[[基底动脉|基底动脉]]和[[大脑中动脉|大脑中动脉]]有时也被认为是Willis环的一部分<ref>Moore KL, Dalley AR. ''Clinically Oriented Anatomy'', 5th Ed., Lippincott Williams & Wilkins, Toronto. Copyright 2007</ref>。

===生理意义===
Willis环可以对供应脑组织的动脉进行血液调配，防止脑血液循环的过剩或不足。当组成Willis环的某一动脉或某一部分出现阻塞或者狭窄，可以通过调节其他血管的血流量弥补缺少的部分，保证脑的血流灌注，避免出现[[缺血|缺血]]的症状，维持脑的营养和机能活动<ref>{{cite journal | author = Boorder, Michiel J.| title = Spect measurements of regional cerebral perfusion and [[carbon_dioxide|carbon dioxide]] reactivity: Correlation with cerebral collaterals in internal carotid artery occlusive disease | journal = J Neurol | volume = 253| issue = 10| pages = 1285–1291| year = 2006| pmid = 17063318| doi = 10.1007/s00415-006-0192-1 | last2 = Van Der Grond | first2 = J | last3 = Van Dongen | first3 = AJ | last4 = Klijn | first4 = CJ | last5 = Jaap Kappelle | first5 = L | last6 = Van Rijk | first6 = PP | last7 = Hendrikse | first7 = J}}</ref>。

===解剖变异===
Willis环存在大量的解剖变异情况。在一项对1413个大脑的解剖研究中，只有34.5%的对象拥有经典的Willis环解剖结构。大部分解剖变异有一个共同的特征：大脑后动脉近端部分狭窄，而其同侧后交通动脉增大，使得颈内动脉供应后脑组织。另外一个常见的解剖变异是前交通动脉变成一条大血管，而单一一条颈内动脉供应两条大脑前动脉<ref>Bergman RA, Afifi AK, Miyauchi R, Circle of Willis. [http://www.vh.org/adult/provider/anatomy/AnatomicVariants/AnatomyHP.html Illustrated Encyclopedia of Human Anatomic Variation] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vh.org/adult/provider/anatomy/AnatomicVariants/AnatomyHP.html |date=20060101024350 }}, URL: [http://www.anatomyatlases.org/AnatomicVariants/Cardiovascular/Text/Arteries/CircleofWillis.shtml http://www.anatomyatlases.org/AnatomicVariants/Cardiovascular/Text/Arteries/CircleofWillis.shtml] {{Wayback|url=http://www.anatomyatlases.org/AnatomicVariants/Cardiovascular/Text/Arteries/CircleofWillis.shtml |date=20210503231659 }}. Accessed on November 6, 2005.</ref>。

===组成血管的起源===
[[Image:Cerebral_angiography,_arteria_vertebralis_sinister_injection.JPG|right]]

左、右颈内动脉分别起自左、右[[颈总动脉|颈总动脉]]。

后交通动脉在颈内动脉分出终末支（即大脑前动脉和大脑中脑动脉）之前不远处分出。

左、右大脑后动脉起源自由左，右[[椎动脉|椎动脉]]组成的基底动脉。椎动脉又起源于[[锁骨下动脉|锁骨下动脉]]。

前交通动脉连接左、右两条大脑前动脉。

所有动脉都和Willis环大脑皮质和中间分支有关。中间分支负责供应Willis环内部即[[脚间窝|脚间窝]]。皮质分支根据它们供应的部位命名，由于它们对Willis环没有直接影响，这里仅作简略介绍。

==病理状态==
===锁骨下动脉盗血综合征===
Willis环组成血管血液供应不足可以导致脑血流灌注减少<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Klingelhöfer | first1 = J | last2 = Conrad | first2 = B | last3 = Benecke | first3 = R | last4 = Frank | first4 = B | title = Transcranial Doppler ultrasonography of carotid-basilar collateral circulation in subclavian steal | journal = Stroke; a journal of cerebral circulation | volume = 19 | issue = 8 | pages = 1036–42 | year = 1988 | pmid = 3041649 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Lord | first1 = RS | last2 = Adar | first2 = R | last3 = Stein | first3 = RL | title = Contribution of the circle of Willis to the subclavian steal syndrome | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_circulation_1969-12_40_6/page/871 | journal = Circulation | volume = 40 | issue = 6 | pages = 871–8 | year = 1969 | pmid = 5377222 }}</ref>。如[[锁骨下动脉盗血综合征|锁骨下动脉盗血综合征]]的患者，锁骨下动脉或[[头臂干|头臂干]]椎动脉起始处近端部分狭窄或闭塞，由于[[虹吸|虹吸效应]]，可以“偷窃”Willis环的血液使其流向上肢，患者可以出现头昏、眼花、恶心、[[呕吐|呕吐]]、[[昏厥|昏厥]]等脑供血症状。

